title: Hyper-V VM VHD
agents: windows
catalog: os/storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk

description:
 This check monitors the attached virtual disks of a virtual machines running on a Microsoft Hyper-V cluster.

 The check queries a Microsoft Hyper-V cluster via an agent plug-in and reports
 the VHD configuration details. It monitors Fixed disks and the maximum image size of each. The check provides
 detailed information about the disk configuration of each virtual machine.

item:
 The virtual machine name as discovered by the agent.

inventory:
 One service for each Fixed virtual disk of a virtual machine is created.
